Title: 'Democracy on tour '
DateModified: '2019-03-05'
DatePublished: '2019-03-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/democracy-on-tour
SetInCountry: India
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: rahul chaudhary
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "The story is about the hypothetical situation of largest democracy of the world..\
  \ \n\nAs per the current demographic and economic trends, technological advancements\
  \ leads India to the unknown but anticipated future where people have invented entirely\
  \ new methods of practicing all the Democratic Republic functions.. \n\nPeople,\
  \ in the advent of applications of most modernized technical equipment including\
  \ the artificial intelligence have started ignoring the core issues including the\
  \ environment degradation..they just have become addicted of many such gadgets...\
  \ \n\nSituation have dramatically worsen when some of the young poor students realized\
  \ that some capitalist morons have fooled the entire civilization by using technical\
  \ gadgets and they started protesting against the National Policies which favoured\
  \ these industrialists..."
